3. Visit the Profile screen, change the user avatar, then check the locked achievements on the Achievements screen.

P = point to the menu icon
BB = click on the menu icon
M = time to think about where to press to find the profile section
P = point to the profile icon
BB = click on the profileicon
M = time to think about where to press to change avatar overlay
P = point to the profile picture icon
BB = click on the profile picture icon
P = point to the upload button
BB = click on the upload button
M = time to think about which image to choose
P = point to the image
BB = select it
BB = upload it
BB = press save
M = time to think about where to see more achievements
P = point to the achievements icon
BB = click an achievement icon
